description: GIVE YOUR BATHROOM A TOUCH OF UNBRIDLED ELEGANCE

Our rectangular tissue box cover combines timeless style with contemporary patterns to create an upscale look that will turn your bathroom’s décor from simple to sensational. We’ve combined a truly unique Milano pattern with Natural Mosaic Capiz that exude an elegantly clean look that complements any décor. Perfectly sized, this tissue box cover is great for any bathroom. It’s great for smaller spaces but still has the presence that fills even the grandest bathrooms. Start building your collection piece by piece and create bathroom décor worthy of a lifestyle magazine cover!

This isn’t just any rectangular tissue box cover, it’s one of the most durable ones around. We’ve primarily used high-grade resin to craft the tisseu box cover, known for its incredible lasting properties. The superior-quality resin doesn’t easily break like regular plastic, and has zero risk of corrosion unlike most metals. So even in the humid conditions of your bathroom, you’re guaranteed of a rectangular tissue box cover that will remain in great  condition. A couple of years down the line and every piece will look as breathtaking as the day you got it!
Here’s why you’ll love the milano rectangular tissue box cover:
- Predominantly mother of Pearl styling that complements any décor.
- Natural Mosaic Capiz add an unmistakably sophisticated touch.
- Made using high-grade resin to ensure maximum durability.
- Perfectly-sized tissue box cover to fit even tight-spaced bathrooms.
- Unique design makes it a great gift for both men and women.
Count on the Milano tissue box cover to lavish your bathroom with uncompromising style
